quran[9{c,v,t}:
30,16,aur jinhon ne kufarkiya aur hamari aayton aur akhirat ke anay ko jhtlaya. woh azaab mein daaley jayen ge
30,17,to jis waqt tum ko shaam ho aur jis waqt subah ho khuda ki tasbeeh karo ( yani namaz parho )
30,18,aur asmano aur zameen mein usi ki tareef hai. aur teesray pehar bhi aur jab dopehar ho ( uss waqt bhi namaz parha karo )
30,19,wohi zinday ko murdy se nkalta aur ( wohi ) murdy ko zinday se nkalta hai aur ( wohi ) zameen ko is ke marnay ke baad zindah karta hai. aur isi terhan tum ( dobarah zameen mein se ) nikalay jao ge
30,20,aur isi ke nishanaat ( aur tasarufaat ) mein se hai ke uss ne tumhe matti se pedakiya. phir ab tum ensaan hokar ja baja phail rahay ho
30,21,aur isi ke nishanaat ( aur tasarufaat ) mein se hai ke uss ne tumahray liye tumhari hi jins ki aurtain peda kee taakay unn ki taraf ( mael hokar ) aaraam haasil karo aur tum mein mohabbat aur meharbani peda kar di jo log ghhor karte hain unn ke liye un baton mein ( bohat si ) nishanain hain
30,22,aur isi ke nishanaat ( aur tasarufaat ) mein se hai asmano aur zameen ka peda karna aur tumhari zabanon aur rangon ka judda judda hona. ehley Danish ke liye un ( baton ) mein ( bohat si ) nishanain hain
30,23,aur isi ke nishanaat ( aur tasarufaat ) mein se hai tumhara raat aur din mein sona aur uss ke fazl ka talaash karna. jo log suntay hain unn ke liye un baton mein ( bohat si ) nishanain hain
30,24,aur isi ke nishanaat ( aur tasarufaat ) mein se hai ke tum ko khauf aur umeed dilanay ke liye bijli dekhata hai aur aasman semeinhہ brsata hai. phir zameen ko is ke mar jaane ke baad zindah ( o shadaab ) kar deta hai. aqal walon ke liye un ( baton ) mein ( bohat si ) nishanain hain
